<section class="ftco-section ftco-no-pb">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="row">
            <div class="col-md-6 img img-3 d-flex justify-content-center align-items-center"
                 style="background-image: url(../../Assets/images/about.jpg);">
            </div>
            <div class="col-md-6 wrap-about pl-md-5 ftco-animate py-5">
                <div class="heading-section">
                    <span class="subheading">Since 2020</span>
                    <h2 class="mb-4" style="font-size: 35px;">Survival Game<br>サバイバルゲーム</h2>

                    <p>
                        A strategy game that simulates military. Similar to Paintball, use air gun shoot to knock opponents out, complete set tasks.<br>
                        <br>過程中講究戰術、地形遊走與射擊反應等軍事技能，刺激且靈活多變，廣受軍事迷的愛戴。
                    </p>
                    <h5 style="margin: 40px 0 20px 0;">玩家必讀<br>正確防護與配戴護目鏡、護具</h5>
                    <!-- <p class="year">
                        <strong class="number" data-number="115">0</strong>
                        <span>Years of Experience In Business</span>
                    </p> -->
                    <p>遊戲首要的考量就是安全，因是模擬戰場上肅殺的環境與氣氛，玩家的安全絕對是擺在第一位。</p>
                    <p style="text-indent: -10px; margin-left: 20px;"><i class="fas fa-genderless" style="margin-right: 10px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>護目鏡的保護，可防止眼睛中彈受傷與失明的風險，以抵擋近距槍擊的傷害。</p>
                    <p style="text-indent: -10px; margin-left: 20px;"><i class="fas fa-genderless" style="margin-right: 10px;" aria-hidden="true"></i>穿戴彈性良好的護膝與手套，就能防止擦傷、挫傷。</p>
                </div>

            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

